            Mediacom Broadband is a division of Mediacom Communications Corporation, one of the nation's leading cable operators focused on serving smaller cities and towns in the United States. The company offers a wide array of broadband products and services, including traditional analog and digital video services and enhanced video products and services, such as video-on-demand, high-definition television and digital video recorders. The company also offers high-speed Internet access and phone service. Using a cable modem, Mediacom Communications Corporation provides Internet access that works far faster than a phone line connection. The company serves more than 1.5 million subscribers in nearly 25 states. Mediacom Broadband maintains a location in Middletown, N.Y.
          






















