Mediacom Broadband LLC: Private Company Information - Bloomberg









































  





















































































July 22, 2017 3:05 AM ET
Media

Company Overview of Mediacom Broadband LLC



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Mediacom Broadband LLC, through its subsidiaries, operates as a cable company in the United States. It offers video, high-speed data (HSD), and phone services to residential and small- to medium-sized business customers over its hybrid fiber and coaxial cable network. The company’s video services include the programming of local broadcast stations, as well as public, government, and leased access channels; national cable and regional sports networks, foreign-language and international programming, digital music channels, and other specialty programming; video-on-demand services consisting of access to movies, national broadcast and cable network shows, music videos, and locally produced even...
Mediacom Broadband LLC, through its subsidiaries, operates as a cable company in the United States. It offers video, high-speed data (HSD), and phone services to residential and small- to medium-sized business customers over its hybrid fiber and coaxial cable network. The company’s video services include the programming of local broadcast stations, as well as public, government, and leased access channels; national cable and regional sports networks, foreign-language and international programming, digital music channels, and other specialty programming; video-on-demand services consisting of access to movies, national broadcast and cable network shows, music videos, and locally produced events, as well as special event programs; and digital video recorder services that allow customers to record programming to view at their convenience. It offers high-speed Internet access to its HSD customers. The company’s phone services include calling and other features, such as Caller ID, call waiting, call forwarding, and three-way calling. It also provides fiber-based network and transport services to medium- and large-sized businesses, governments, and educational institutions; sells advertising to local, regional, and national advertisers on television and digital platforms under the OnMedia brand name; and offers home security and automation services to residential customers. As of December 31, 2016, Mediacom Broadband LLC served approximately 463,000 video, 643,000 HSD, and 264,000 phone customers. The company was founded in 1995 and is based in New York, New York. Mediacom Broadband LLC is a subsidiary of Mediacom Communications Corporation.
