Mediacom Broadband LLC Key Developments

Mediacom Broadband LLC Reports Unaudited Earnings Results for the First Quarter Ended March 31, 2017
May 3 17
Mediacom Broadband LLC reported unaudited earnings results for the first quarter ended March 31, 2017. For the quarter, the company reported total revenues of $261,508,000 against $255,218,000 a year ago. OIBDA was $99,279,000 against $98,425,000 a year ago. Capital expenditures were $46,037,000 against $42,345,000 a year ago. Net cash flows provided by operating activities were $81,071,000 against $94,403,000 a year ago. Operating income was $62,700,000 against $63,097,000 a year ago.


Mediacom Broadband LLC Reports Unaudited Earnings Results for the Fourth Quarter and Full Year Ended December 31, 2016
Feb 23 17
Mediacom Broadband LLC reported unaudited earnings results for the fourth quarter and full year ended December 31, 2016. For the quarter, the company's total revenues were $262,954,000 compared to $250,863,000 a year ago. OIBDA was $106,245,000 compared to $101,329,000 a year ago. Capital expenditures was $48,216,000 compared to $39,818,000 a year ago. Net cash flows provided by operating activities was $86,022,000 compared to $75,398,000 a year ago. Operating income was $67,288,000 compared to $65,235,000 a year ago.

For the year, the company's total revenues were $1,033,239,000 compared to $982,362,000 a year ago. OIBDA was $399,364,000 compared to $379,467,000 a year ago. Capital expenditures was $179,696,000 compared to $151,204,000 a year ago. Net cash flows provided by operating activities was $336,034,000 compared to $297,236,000 a year ago. Operating income was $252,250,000 compared to $235,247,000 a year ago.


Mediacom Broadband LLC Reports Unaudited Earnings Results for the Third Quarter Ended September 30, 2016
Nov 1 16
Mediacom Broadband LLC reported unaudited earnings results for the third quarter ended September 30, 2016. For the quarter, the company reported total revenues of $258,699,000 against $245,414,000 a year ago. OIBDA was $96,622,000 against $91,721,000 a year ago. Capital expenditures were $44,122,000 against $36,156,000 a year ago. Free cash flow was $30,084,000 against $29,168,000 a year ago. Net cash flows provided by operating activities were $80,521,000 against $74,742,000 a year ago. Operating income was $59,368,000 against $55,721,000 a year ago.


