Business Summary




Mediacom Broadband LLC operates an interactive broadband network which provides its residential and commercial customers with a wide variety of products and services, including the Company's primary services of video, HSD and phone, which it refers to as its “triple-play” bundle. The Company also provides network and transport services to medium and large sized businesses in its service areas, including cell tower backhaul for wireless telephone providers, and sell advertising time we receive under our programming license agreements to local, regional and national advertisers.


