About Mediacom Communications

Mediacom the local cable company that serves more than 1,500 communities across the country. Mediacom is the largest cable company in Iowa and second largest in Illinois. Examples of cities with Mediacom service include Albany, Georgia, Columbus, Georgia, Tifton, Georgia, and Valdosta, Georgia, Ames, Iowa, Cedar Rapids, Iowa and Des Moines, Iowa, Quad Cities on the border between Iowa / Illinois; Columbia, Missouri, Jefferson City, Missouri, and Springfield, Missouri. Mediacom also serves outlying areas of the Gulf Coast of Florida and around Minneapolis, Minnesota.
